00:00:01.940 --> 00:00:05.879
Well, the Kafka Client Libraries and Kafka Connect

00:00:05.879 --> 00:00:08.504
will be sufficient for most Kafka integrations.

00:00:08.505 --> 00:00:12.915
There are times where existing systems will be unable to use either approach.

00:00:12.914 --> 00:00:17.099
In these cases, any client that can manage HTTP requests can

00:00:17.100 --> 00:00:22.125
integrate with Kafka over HTTP REST using the Kafka REST proxy.

00:00:22.125 --> 00:00:24.359
This section you'll learn how rest proxy

00:00:24.359 --> 00:00:27.789
works and how it can help you in these scenarios.

